1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,560
As I always say, I handle the full life cycle.

2
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:07,360
You know that line, right?

3
00:00:07,360 --> 00:00:09,840
I design, I implement, I ship.

4
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:18,560
Well, I help design, I implement certain components, and I ship some features.

5
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:21,600
The life cycle is a team thing.

6
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:27,560
So when I say I handled it, I mean I handled part of it.

7
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:29,560
It's cleaner to tell it like that.

